17/11/2004
TIRANA, Albania -- President Alfred Moisiu met on Tuesday (16 November) with the head of the European Commission delegation in Tirana, Lutz Salzman, to discuss the EU-funded police reform project. Officials of the Police Assistance Mission of the European Community in Albania also attended. The objective of the project is to establish a state police force in line with European standards. (Albanian Daily News - 17/11/04)
